Popular actress Iyabo Ojo has urged spouses of movie practitioners and actors precisely to procure shock absorbers. The movie star made this suggestion as she argued actors are generally never faithful to their partners. She spoke in a chat with popular OAP, Daddy Freeze alongside her US-based colleague, Victoria Inyama. Their chat was precipitated by the news of Yul Edochie announcing a second wife and baby The revelation sparked an uproar among celebrities and social media users.   ‘Most ladies condemning polygamy date married…     Meet Yul Edochie’s second wife     Only illiterates fart before partners – Bobrisky   While speaking on fidelity among men especially actors, Iyabo Ojo stressed she has never seen a faithful actor in Nollywood. She further advised everyone married to an actor to purchase a shock absorber because infidelity among actors is a normal lifestyle even though many try to pretend about it. “Men cheat. Victoria you should not be surprised, you know how the industry is. It’s very hard for an actor in Nigeria I’ve never seen a faithful actor. It’s a fact. Do you know how women, girls flock around these actors? “Anybody that is married to an actor should always have…should go and buy what they call shock absorber. Because it’ normal, it’s very difficult. We always just pretend,” Ojo said.